u}^{SM}+ a_{
u}^{O_W}$, $\langle r^2_{
u} angle ^{eff} = \langle r^2_{
u} angle ^{SM}+\langle r^2_{
u} angle ^{O_W}$)is gotten, just as in the SM. Using the experimental constraint on the anomalous $WW\gamma$ vertex, a value for the additional contribution to the charge radius of $|\langle r^2_{
